data.description: This is a must see!  Providence Point for less than $400k?  Are you kidding me?  No, we are absolutely serious! All of the hardwood, tile floors, solid surface counters, fireplace, upgraded electrical fixtures you have come to enjoy in a PP home without the large price tag.  Sit on your screened porch on those fall mornings and listen to the nature sounds.  Come see this one quickly I'm getting calls already!  Please give a 24 hour notice due to the homeowner's work schedule.
